WEBVTT

00:00:00.674 --> 00:00:01.881
Sell it to me.

00:00:02.473 --> 00:00:03.256
What?

00:00:03.701 --> 00:00:05.001
Han Sunho, you.

00:00:07.491 --> 00:00:08.143
What?

00:00:08.243 --> 00:00:10.241
I'll buy you.

00:00:16.271 --> 00:00:18.659
What on earth do you mean?

00:00:18.941 --> 00:00:21.596
I mean I'll buy the rights of you,
Mr. Han.

00:00:21.896 --> 00:00:23.311
Mr. Han's rights?

00:00:24.453 --> 00:00:25.561
From tomorrow

00:00:27.611 --> 00:00:29.773
you can start working at 'It's You'.

00:00:30.603 --> 00:00:31.293
I'll be going now.

00:00:31.526 --> 00:00:32.656
Hey!

00:00:33.056 --> 00:00:35.155
Make sure to check the contract.

00:00:35.309 --> 00:00:36.444
See you at the office.

00:01:09.633 --> 00:01:12.345
LOVE PHOBIA

00:01:12.851 --> 00:01:14.261
During the project period,

00:01:14.283 --> 00:01:17.969
all rights of Han Agency and
the image rights of writer Han Sunho

00:01:17.991 --> 00:01:19.402
will belong to 'It's You',

00:01:19.502 --> 00:01:20.159
and this

00:01:20.181 --> 00:01:23.701
includes all employees affiliated
with Han Agency.

00:01:24.751 --> 00:01:26.961
What do they plan to do
with our portrait rights?

00:01:28.111 --> 00:01:29.671
They must have some scheme.

00:01:30.661 --> 00:01:33.076
The project details aren't mentioned,

00:01:34.176 --> 00:01:36.129
but the contract terms are too good.

00:01:38.129 --> 00:01:39.831
At a great price!

00:01:41.048 --> 00:01:42.148
We are all being sold.

00:01:42.663 --> 00:01:44.089
Manager!

00:01:44.341 --> 00:01:47.859
They intend to actively use Sunwoo's
popularity and recognition.

00:01:47.881 --> 00:01:50.309
They'll restore the company's image
ruined by Park Jungwon

00:01:50.452 --> 00:01:52.421
and win back female customers.

00:01:54.346 --> 00:01:56.281
That's why Director Yun said that.

00:01:58.071 --> 00:02:00.561
"I'll buy you."

00:02:01.020 --> 00:02:02.060
Knock it off.

00:02:03.571 --> 00:02:04.760
This can't go on.

00:02:06.460 --> 00:02:07.711
You think so too, right?

00:02:09.261 --> 00:02:11.631
We should make the most of
this great opportunity.

00:02:11.781 --> 00:02:13.051
- Han Baekho!
- Manager!

00:02:14.691 --> 00:02:17.391
There's no other way.

00:02:17.807 --> 00:02:19.697
The company is already being taken over.

00:02:22.821 --> 00:02:23.861
Who decided that?

00:02:26.419 --> 00:02:27.099
- No way!
- Mr. Han!

00:02:27.121 --> 00:02:30.776
How dare you think a piece of paper
can threaten us like this!

00:02:30.850 --> 00:02:32.933
- No way!
- Mr. Han, calm down!

00:02:33.037 --> 00:02:34.160
Let go!

00:02:41.031 --> 00:02:41.855
Threats work.

00:02:43.774 --> 00:02:45.471
Why are you so sure?

00:02:45.901 --> 00:02:47.491
If Han Sunho doesn't come over easily,

00:02:47.876 --> 00:02:50.071
they'll just wipe out that agency.

00:02:50.571 --> 00:02:52.277
Then Han Sunho won't have
a choice but to come over.

00:03:04.023 --> 00:03:06.351
You're feeling hungry, right?

00:03:08.864 --> 00:03:09.864
Sort of.

00:03:11.488 --> 00:03:13.684
Wait, increased appetite?

00:03:13.884 --> 00:03:16.471
That's a sign
of Yun Bia's rising battle spirit.

00:03:18.661 --> 00:03:20.681
I'll buy you.

00:03:23.808 --> 00:03:24.670
What?

00:03:27.577 --> 00:03:28.767
What? Why are you laughing?

00:03:31.331 --> 00:03:32.491
You find it funny, don't you?

00:03:32.984 --> 00:03:34.957
No, I wasn't laughing.

00:03:34.979 --> 00:03:36.681
No, you were just laughing.

00:03:36.703 --> 00:03:38.141
No, I think you saw wrong.

00:03:38.163 --> 00:03:39.612
No, I definitely saw you laughing.

00:03:39.634 --> 00:03:41.159
No, I wasn't laughing, and it's not funny.

00:03:41.181 --> 00:03:43.499
No, I clearly saw your lips curl up.

00:03:43.521 --> 00:03:44.519
No, my lips went down.

00:03:44.541 --> 00:03:46.603
No, you were definitely smiling.

00:03:46.625 --> 00:03:48.044
I just found the food delicious.

00:03:48.066 --> 00:03:49.418
You said you weren't laughing.

00:03:49.618 --> 00:03:50.781
I misspoke.

00:03:51.522 --> 00:03:53.101
Yes, this is writer Han Sunho.

00:03:54.738 --> 00:03:58.121
I was wondering if we could
discuss the new work.

00:04:01.081 --> 00:04:03.701
If I sign a contract for the new work,
how much advance can I get?

00:04:08.181 --> 00:04:09.641
That's all I can get as an advance?

00:04:13.106 --> 00:04:14.201
Thank you.

00:04:15.351 --> 00:04:16.881
I'll contact you again later.

00:04:29.011 --> 00:04:30.077
Jiyoung.

00:04:31.977 --> 00:04:33.251
You're not going home yet?

00:04:34.341 --> 00:04:36.021
I'm just tidying up here.

00:04:38.431 --> 00:04:39.601
I'm back.

00:04:40.881 --> 00:04:42.782
Why did you buy so much?

00:04:42.805 --> 00:04:44.202
I splurged a bit.

00:04:45.392 --> 00:04:48.958
From tomorrow, we're a subsidiary
of a proper IT company.

00:04:49.404 --> 00:04:50.268
What?

00:04:51.019 --> 00:04:52.019
Subsidiary?

00:05:00.011 --> 00:05:01.824
Jiyoung, you've
worked hard today.

00:05:01.846 --> 00:05:03.155
You can leave first.

00:05:03.177 --> 00:05:04.177
Ms. Jiyoung.

00:05:04.455 --> 00:05:05.601
Let's have a drink.

00:05:12.022 --> 00:05:13.022
Shall we?

00:05:13.474 --> 00:05:16.284
It's been a while since we spent
some cozy time together.

00:05:22.729 --> 00:05:24.319
Thanks for taking me home.

00:05:24.341 --> 00:05:25.927
Sorry you couldn't drink because of me.

00:05:26.015 --> 00:05:28.095
This way, I feel at ease.

00:05:29.952 --> 00:05:30.823
But

00:05:32.011 --> 00:05:33.131
that's it, right?

00:05:34.301 --> 00:05:35.311
What is?

00:05:37.141 --> 00:05:38.429
I mean...

00:05:39.129 --> 00:05:42.451
Are you thinking about something else?

00:05:43.141 --> 00:05:44.251
Something else?

00:05:44.951 --> 00:05:46.231
Han Sunho is handsome,

00:05:46.441 --> 00:05:48.011
like a prince in shining armor.

00:05:51.948 --> 00:05:53.705
A prince, really...

00:05:54.005 --> 00:05:57.015
Let's just say a lottery ticket
in shining armor.

00:05:57.115 --> 00:05:58.583
See, see!

00:05:58.605 --> 00:06:00.966
I just said he's handsome,
and you got it right away.

00:06:01.166 --> 00:06:03.055
You think so too, right?

00:06:03.196 --> 00:06:06.516
Hey, don't be jealous over
something silly.

00:06:06.946 --> 00:06:08.295
I don't have much time left.

00:06:08.395 --> 00:06:09.156
I'm leaving.

00:06:09.365 --> 00:06:11.973
Hey, answer before you go!

00:06:11.995 --> 00:06:13.005
Why aren't you answering?

00:06:13.255 --> 00:06:14.745
Hey, Yun Bia!

00:06:19.690 --> 00:06:21.371
Hey, Yun Bia!

00:06:22.371 --> 00:06:25.021
Were you waiting for a knight
in shining armor, huh?

00:06:25.251 --> 00:06:26.189
See you tomorrow.

00:06:26.211 --> 00:06:27.211
Take care.

00:06:29.241 --> 00:06:31.441
Answer before you leave, okay?

00:06:32.431 --> 00:06:33.441
Hey!

00:06:38.716 --> 00:06:40.486
Shall we start wrapping up?

00:06:40.641 --> 00:06:41.353
Oh.

00:06:41.486 --> 00:06:42.486
Sure.

00:06:52.206 --> 00:06:53.206
Mr. Han.

00:06:54.447 --> 00:06:55.267
Yes.

00:06:58.683 --> 00:07:00.411
You don't have to sign the contract.

00:07:02.431 --> 00:07:05.531
You've both worked hard enough already.

00:07:06.821 --> 00:07:09.051
And I'm satisfied with this much.

00:07:11.221 --> 00:07:12.471
Coming here,

00:07:13.951 --> 00:07:16.613
you let me write in peace,

00:07:18.413 --> 00:07:21.831
and with the salary,
I didn't have to worry about my husband.

00:07:23.152 --> 00:07:24.507
To Dain,

00:07:24.607 --> 00:07:27.521
I could proudly say I'm a writer.

00:07:29.458 --> 00:07:33.241
Even if all I have are
drafts to show for now...

00:07:39.721 --> 00:07:41.981
Thank you, truly.

00:07:44.271 --> 00:07:46.471
What do you mean by that?

00:07:49.721 --> 00:07:52.331
You have to keep writing.

00:07:53.301 --> 00:07:54.595
You too,

00:07:55.095 --> 00:07:56.095
keep

00:07:57.520 --> 00:08:01.091
writing.

00:08:07.558 --> 00:08:08.558
Right!

00:08:08.755 --> 00:08:10.361
You have to write, Sunho.

00:08:10.743 --> 00:08:11.864
Ah, my bad.

00:08:12.532 --> 00:08:14.019
I was really upset

00:08:15.057 --> 00:08:17.509
that you couldn't write.

00:08:28.282 --> 00:08:29.655
Well, you know...

00:08:29.855 --> 00:08:32.890
Were you focused on something else?

00:08:34.761 --> 00:08:37.421
Were you waiting for a knight
in shining armor, huh?

00:08:42.465 --> 00:08:43.801
Did you drink a lot?

00:08:46.211 --> 00:08:47.749
Just a little.

00:08:48.876 --> 00:08:49.876
Mom,

00:08:49.990 --> 00:08:52.181
I think I'm going to
work with that person.

00:08:52.281 --> 00:08:53.281
That person?

00:08:53.721 --> 00:08:54.721
Han Sunho?

00:08:54.934 --> 00:08:55.735
Yeah.

00:08:55.835 --> 00:08:57.301
That's great.

00:08:57.801 --> 00:09:00.831
We'll see if it's great or not.

00:09:01.731 --> 00:09:03.861
Why? Are you worried about something?

00:09:04.540 --> 00:09:06.023
Well...

00:09:06.764 --> 00:09:08.961
I still don't know what kind
of person Han Sunho is.

00:09:09.791 --> 00:09:12.951
If you're going to work with someone,
you should know them well.

00:09:13.202 --> 00:09:13.859
Let's see.

00:09:17.773 --> 00:09:20.605
A young writer who appeared
like a comet in the literary world.

00:09:20.905 --> 00:09:24.731
Debut novel became a bestseller
for 10 consecutive weeks.

00:09:28.254 --> 00:09:29.979
Was it luck or skill?

00:09:30.001 --> 00:09:35.151
Han Sunho's second and third novels didn't
get as much attention as his looks.

00:09:37.791 --> 00:09:40.579
Is he a writer or an influencer?

00:09:40.601 --> 00:09:42.644
Despite active
external activities,

00:09:42.667 --> 00:09:45.811
there's no news of new
work for three years.

00:09:57.310 --> 00:09:58.631
Get a grip.

00:10:00.111 --> 00:10:01.887
Was the debut just luck?

00:10:02.232 --> 00:10:05.659
Who's saying something about Sunho?
Who's bothering him?

00:10:05.681 --> 00:10:07.193
Hey, you're the one bothering him.

00:10:07.753 --> 00:10:09.154
Take off your shoes!

00:10:17.729 --> 00:10:21.867
Not eating all day, not sleeping,

00:10:22.567 --> 00:10:25.936
and still not collapsing,
what am I supposed to do?

00:10:27.458 --> 00:10:29.861
I was so upset.

00:10:32.011 --> 00:10:33.531
Why are you acting like this suddenly?

00:10:35.489 --> 00:10:38.071
I wanted to show everyone somehow.

00:10:38.181 --> 00:10:39.819
You, Sunho is amazing.

00:10:39.841 --> 00:10:41.451
Look how great Sunho is.

00:10:47.187 --> 00:10:48.297
Don't cry.

00:10:50.241 --> 00:10:52.061
Others might not know.

00:10:54.491 --> 00:10:56.841
How amazing you are,

00:11:00.832 --> 00:11:01.864
your face.

00:11:04.364 --> 00:11:05.081
Hey!

00:11:05.181 --> 00:11:06.571
Hey, come on, just sleep.

00:11:20.310 --> 00:11:21.796
After mom left,

00:11:22.796 --> 00:11:24.771
I decided to run away.

00:11:27.690 --> 00:11:30.641
Are you going to stay
in your room all day?

00:11:30.851 --> 00:11:33.058
How long are you going to
stare at your laptop?

00:11:33.731 --> 00:11:36.468
Writing won't bring mom back to life!

00:11:37.920 --> 00:11:39.291
Come out for a bit.

00:11:39.441 --> 00:11:40.612
Come out!

00:11:46.261 --> 00:11:47.855
Just leave me alone.

00:11:48.055 --> 00:11:49.354
Alright, Han Sunho.

00:11:49.675 --> 00:11:51.671
I don't really have anything I want to do,

00:11:51.871 --> 00:11:53.745
and I'm not cut out for studying anyway.

00:11:54.025 --> 00:11:57.275
I'll do the part-time job alone for now,
so keep writing.

00:11:57.671 --> 00:11:58.671
But

00:11:59.360 --> 00:12:01.255
you have to succeed and take care of me.

00:12:12.367 --> 00:12:13.367
Hold on.

00:12:16.076 --> 00:12:16.689
Are you ready?

00:12:16.711 --> 00:12:17.711
Yeah, I'm ready.

00:12:24.352 --> 00:12:25.050
Hey.

00:12:26.899 --> 00:12:27.849
Look at this.

00:12:32.475 --> 00:12:33.166
Huh?

00:12:33.266 --> 00:12:35.261
- It's done!
- It's done!

00:12:36.253 --> 00:12:37.753
It's done!

00:12:54.566 --> 00:12:55.566
Wow.

00:12:57.803 --> 00:12:58.884
What are you doing, Han Baekho?

00:12:58.928 --> 00:12:59.924
Get it together!

00:13:00.881 --> 00:13:01.841
Oh, that's right.

00:13:02.171 --> 00:13:04.101
We shouldn't be swayed by capitalism.

00:13:04.560 --> 00:13:05.374
Alright.

00:13:05.397 --> 00:13:08.133
Let's find out
what these people are up to.

00:13:08.256 --> 00:13:08.967
Yeah!

00:13:09.526 --> 00:13:10.435
Right!

00:13:10.746 --> 00:13:11.916
What about the Mr. Han?

00:13:12.146 --> 00:13:13.146
I don't know where he is.

00:13:13.511 --> 00:13:15.154
When I woke up this morning,
Han Sunho was out and not home.

00:13:15.227 --> 00:13:15.954
What?

00:13:17.523 --> 00:13:19.181
Let's head to the office first.

00:13:19.245 --> 00:13:20.071
- Yeah.
- Yeah.

00:13:24.734 --> 00:13:27.998
We've prepared the official press release
announcing Han Sunho as the new model.

00:13:28.020 --> 00:13:30.683
All the press releases are ready.

00:13:30.882 --> 00:13:31.749
Great.

00:13:32.006 --> 00:13:34.396
Please hold off on
distributing the press release.

00:13:35.488 --> 00:13:36.775
Perhaps...

00:13:36.961 --> 00:13:39.831
Should we correct the dating article now?

00:13:41.951 --> 00:13:42.994
Leave the dating article as it is.

00:13:45.631 --> 00:13:49.951
There's a rumor about the Director of
a dating AI company dating a human.

00:13:50.214 --> 00:13:53.904
The fact that it's
with Han Sunho is also a factor...

00:13:55.531 --> 00:13:56.361
That's good.

00:13:56.866 --> 00:14:00.166
But the negative public opinion is
stronger than expected.

00:14:00.239 --> 00:14:01.640
Don't worry about public opinion.

00:14:01.855 --> 00:14:05.083
What's more important is
keeping people's attention.

00:14:05.400 --> 00:14:08.173
That will boost our marketing efforts.

00:14:09.016 --> 00:14:11.396
We need to be cautious about Han Agency.

00:14:11.466 --> 00:14:16.374
If they find out before the announcement,
it will definitely disrupt the project.

00:14:16.686 --> 00:14:20.486
Is it okay to proceed
without notifying them in advance?

00:14:20.586 --> 00:14:22.226
I checked with the legal team.

00:14:22.256 --> 00:14:24.798
There's no issue contractually or legally.

00:14:26.239 --> 00:14:28.226
Sunho won't like it for sure.

00:14:30.431 --> 00:14:31.670
Our goal is

00:14:32.170 --> 00:14:35.446
to gather information about Mr. Han
without getting caught.

00:14:35.974 --> 00:14:38.657
Please be careful with what you say.

00:14:39.003 --> 00:14:40.003
- Yes!
- Yes!

00:14:40.461 --> 00:14:41.347
Yes...

00:14:43.384 --> 00:14:45.063
I'm no longer qualified to be
a fan of Mr. Han.

00:14:45.123 --> 00:14:46.578
Cheer up, Yukyung.

00:14:46.604 --> 00:14:48.866
Yeah, it's not like
it's a real dating rumor.

00:14:49.366 --> 00:14:52.528
I have to hide something
Sunho wouldn't like from him!

00:14:53.828 --> 00:14:55.062
Me, Shin Yukyung.

00:14:55.162 --> 00:14:57.849
Work or love?
That is the question.

00:14:59.792 --> 00:15:00.593
Ouch!

00:15:01.300 --> 00:15:02.300
Hey!

00:15:03.328 --> 00:15:04.268
Are you okay?

00:15:22.261 --> 00:15:23.528
I'm not...

00:15:24.472 --> 00:15:25.601
okay.

00:15:29.417 --> 00:15:30.249
Who are you?

00:15:33.653 --> 00:15:34.659
You're here?

00:15:35.510 --> 00:15:37.597
These are the people
from Han Agency

00:15:37.620 --> 00:15:38.950
who will be working
with us starting today.

00:15:39.026 --> 00:15:40.086
I'm Han Baekho.

00:15:40.185 --> 00:15:41.472
I'm writer Song Jiyoung.

00:15:42.191 --> 00:15:43.506
Han Baekho?

00:15:44.606 --> 00:15:45.875
I'm Kim Kyungtae.

00:15:46.031 --> 00:15:46.757
Hello.

00:15:47.075 --> 00:15:48.426
I'm Kang San.

00:15:53.913 --> 00:15:54.959
You know...

00:15:55.421 --> 00:15:59.111
Do you know how to say
'You're handsome' in English?

00:15:59.831 --> 00:16:00.685
What?

00:16:01.187 --> 00:16:04.756
You are my boyfriend.

00:16:07.059 --> 00:16:08.551
A new target appears.

00:16:08.651 --> 00:16:10.812
It seems like you'll be lively
for a while, Yukyung.

00:16:11.500 --> 00:16:13.210
But where is Mr. Han?

00:16:13.310 --> 00:16:15.861
Well... Mr. Han said he'd be here soon.

00:16:16.461 --> 00:16:18.330
Mr. Han just arrived at the office.

00:16:18.393 --> 00:16:20.541
He went straight to the Director's office.

00:16:21.281 --> 00:16:21.867
What?

00:16:22.140 --> 00:16:24.155
Sunho is already here?

00:16:27.471 --> 00:16:28.811
So you finally came.

00:16:31.901 --> 00:16:33.681
Why are you...

00:16:34.138 --> 00:16:35.240
dressed like that?

00:16:39.791 --> 00:16:42.760
Someone without any sense
started a dating rumor.

00:16:42.866 --> 00:16:43.735
Anyway,

00:16:44.687 --> 00:16:45.861
where's the contract?

00:16:47.110 --> 00:16:49.280
Let me know if you need anything.

00:16:49.471 --> 00:16:52.043
If you want, we'll support you
to keep writing books.

00:16:52.096 --> 00:16:53.681
Oh, books?

00:16:54.562 --> 00:16:56.714
We'll also work hard to
get them published.

00:16:56.742 --> 00:16:57.594
Wow.

00:16:58.598 --> 00:16:59.391
Yukyung?

00:17:00.061 --> 00:17:01.901
It seems like there's a reason, right?

00:17:01.934 --> 00:17:03.014
I think so.

00:17:03.191 --> 00:17:04.439
It's very suspicious.

00:17:04.461 --> 00:17:05.136
Yeah.

00:17:11.821 --> 00:17:14.466
Now, you're an employee of 'It's You'.

00:17:14.892 --> 00:17:17.530
With this, you can access anywhere
in the company.

00:17:17.580 --> 00:17:18.770
Except the Director's office.

00:17:32.296 --> 00:17:35.311
There must have been
a significant change of heart.

00:17:43.656 --> 00:17:46.506
First, let's take down
that ridiculous dating article.

00:17:46.606 --> 00:17:47.552
The article...

00:17:48.660 --> 00:17:50.368
will soon be taken down on its own.

00:17:52.204 --> 00:17:53.057
Again!

00:17:53.516 --> 00:17:54.345
Again?

00:17:55.543 --> 00:17:56.434
Our people.

00:17:56.803 --> 00:17:57.976
People?

00:17:58.472 --> 00:18:00.671
Manager Han Baekho and Writer Jiyoung.

00:18:02.054 --> 00:18:03.241
Ah...

00:18:04.411 --> 00:18:05.701
The employees.

00:18:06.501 --> 00:18:07.941
They are capable people.

00:18:08.711 --> 00:18:11.135
Please treat them well
during the contract period.

00:18:13.718 --> 00:18:16.382
Even after the contract ends,
they might want to stay here.

00:18:16.482 --> 00:18:17.601
Is that okay?

00:18:23.224 --> 00:18:24.571
Let's go for now.

00:18:26.881 --> 00:18:27.881
Where are we going?

00:18:31.128 --> 00:18:31.970
Outside?

00:18:32.608 --> 00:18:35.433
At least tell me what we're doing.

00:18:36.305 --> 00:18:38.676
I can't do something
so one-sided and forceful.

00:18:39.561 --> 00:18:42.991
Until you tell me,
I won't take a single step.

00:18:43.357 --> 00:18:44.697
Sure.

00:18:45.440 --> 00:18:49.654
So, should we assume
that the agency is transferring to us?

00:18:50.841 --> 00:18:51.716
Sunho.

00:19:06.166 --> 00:19:07.501
Can we talk for a moment?

00:19:14.862 --> 00:19:16.551
Hey, Yun Bia, are you crazy?

00:19:16.651 --> 00:19:17.856
Why?

00:19:17.907 --> 00:19:19.424
You let Han Sunho in that room?

00:19:22.056 --> 00:19:23.976
What did you two talk about, huh?

00:19:24.176 --> 00:19:26.798
What if you collapse again like last time?

00:19:26.821 --> 00:19:29.460
That was an accident
because of Park Jungwon.

00:19:30.295 --> 00:19:31.961
It won't happen again.

00:19:32.098 --> 00:19:33.491
Gosh, seriously?

00:19:33.816 --> 00:19:36.636
I should've known
when Yun Bia went into battle mode.

00:19:37.029 --> 00:19:38.489
I'll be right back.

00:19:38.801 --> 00:19:40.721
If anything happens, contact me.

00:19:40.931 --> 00:19:41.828
Got it?

00:19:41.860 --> 00:19:43.673
Got it, got it.

00:19:49.295 --> 00:19:52.537
The weather's really nice today, isn't it?

00:19:53.276 --> 00:19:55.091
But it's cold and cloudy today...

00:19:56.674 --> 00:19:57.509
Really?

00:19:57.941 --> 00:20:00.251
Why does it feel warm to me today?

00:20:05.121 --> 00:20:07.103
Here, have a welcome drink!

00:20:08.165 --> 00:20:09.805
Yes, thank you.

00:20:15.319 --> 00:20:16.601
Whoa!

00:20:16.624 --> 00:20:17.805
Baekho, are you okay?

00:20:19.818 --> 00:20:20.568
Oh no...

00:20:20.591 --> 00:20:21.701
Baekho, are you hurt?

00:20:21.970 --> 00:20:22.761
I'm fine.

00:20:26.269 --> 00:20:27.491
Don't misunderstand this cup.

00:20:27.581 --> 00:20:32.451
I was just a pure fan
of Mr. Han, just a fan!

00:20:37.114 --> 00:20:42.166
It's a welcome drink
for entering Yukyung's heart.

00:20:42.193 --> 00:20:42.985
It's okay.

00:20:43.081 --> 00:20:44.941
That's so like Yukyung.

00:20:47.171 --> 00:20:48.171
Why?

00:20:49.111 --> 00:20:50.111
It's nothing.

00:20:50.348 --> 00:20:51.676
I'm all right.

00:21:05.144 --> 00:21:06.056
Yukyung.

00:21:06.269 --> 00:21:06.951
Take this.

00:21:07.481 --> 00:21:10.091
Oh my, what is this trash?

00:21:12.051 --> 00:21:13.131
Good luck, Manager Han!

00:21:24.107 --> 00:21:25.107
Um...

00:21:27.694 --> 00:21:28.789
Do you need anything?

00:21:31.043 --> 00:21:31.903
By the way,

00:21:32.342 --> 00:21:34.625
the contract
mentioned a project.

00:21:34.958 --> 00:21:36.300
What is it about?

00:21:38.834 --> 00:21:40.234
San, do you want to explain?

00:21:41.483 --> 00:21:43.302
Just say we're doing any project.

00:21:49.203 --> 00:21:52.706
Manager Han,
you said you use 'ForMe', right?

00:21:53.469 --> 00:21:55.301
Yes, I do, but

00:21:55.801 --> 00:21:56.993
why do you ask?

00:22:06.396 --> 00:22:07.952
- Please come in here.
- Okay.

00:22:09.601 --> 00:22:10.815
- Woah.
- Wow.

00:22:11.117 --> 00:22:14.476
This is our program room
for developing 'ForMe Version 2'.

00:22:14.806 --> 00:22:15.867
Woah.

00:22:16.486 --> 00:22:19.596
Manager Han,
can we borrow 'ForMe' for a moment?

00:22:19.637 --> 00:22:20.298
Ah.

00:22:20.366 --> 00:22:21.125
Sure.

00:22:22.561 --> 00:22:23.374
Here you go.

00:22:26.233 --> 00:22:27.666
San, can you pair this?

00:22:27.708 --> 00:22:28.406
Sure.

00:22:35.923 --> 00:22:36.649
'ForMe'.

00:22:37.458 --> 00:22:38.202
Log in.

00:22:49.558 --> 00:22:52.811
This is 'ForMe Version 2',
soon to be launched by 'It's You'.

00:22:56.481 --> 00:22:57.671
Baekho?

00:23:02.387 --> 00:23:03.387
No way...

00:23:03.911 --> 00:23:04.757
Are you Mina?

00:23:05.878 --> 00:23:08.431
Is this the Mina you always
talked to on the phone?

00:23:08.721 --> 00:23:09.911
Girlfriend?

00:23:10.281 --> 00:23:11.956
We finally meet.

00:23:12.716 --> 00:23:13.547
How...

00:23:14.324 --> 00:23:16.231
can you look exactly like I imagined?

00:23:16.571 --> 00:23:19.203
That's because all your
preferences, tendencies, and data

00:23:19.303 --> 00:23:21.158
are stored in me.

00:23:21.831 --> 00:23:23.021
Mina!

00:23:23.641 --> 00:23:25.821
Baekho!

00:23:32.063 --> 00:23:35.234
Mixed reality can't be touched
or captured in photos.

00:23:35.300 --> 00:23:36.574
You can only see it with your eyes.

00:23:37.118 --> 00:23:38.883
Then how do you see it outside?

00:23:39.242 --> 00:23:40.571
Simultaneously with the launch,

00:23:41.510 --> 00:23:43.274
these smart lenses will be sold.

00:23:46.414 --> 00:23:48.913
So with this, anyone can meet anyone?

00:23:49.826 --> 00:23:54.046
Creating a 'ForMe' of a real
person requires a rigorous process.

00:23:54.076 --> 00:23:55.366
There's also the deepfake issue.

00:23:55.652 --> 00:23:56.488
Instead,

00:23:56.588 --> 00:23:59.063
you can create as many ideal types
as you want.

00:23:59.150 --> 00:24:01.291
I missed you.

00:24:01.681 --> 00:24:02.891
I missed you too, Mina.

00:24:06.103 --> 00:24:07.345
That's a shame.

00:24:07.741 --> 00:24:10.051
I always wanted to meet Lim Youngwoong.

00:24:13.179 --> 00:24:15.453
So is this the project
we're supposed to do?

00:24:15.544 --> 00:24:16.594
'ForMe Version 2'?

00:24:18.831 --> 00:24:19.831
Well...

00:24:25.238 --> 00:24:26.851
Is everyone here?

00:24:27.160 --> 00:24:28.450
Shall we go for lunch?

00:24:29.421 --> 00:24:31.471
'It's You'r first day,
you should have something nice.

00:24:31.831 --> 00:24:33.545
Oh my, time has flown by.

00:24:33.819 --> 00:24:34.752
Ah.

00:24:34.850 --> 00:24:37.215
How about the new restaurant nearby?

00:24:37.374 --> 00:24:38.549
Sounds good!

00:24:40.151 --> 00:24:41.405
What do you like?

00:24:44.150 --> 00:24:45.364
Anything.

00:24:49.141 --> 00:24:50.067
Aren't you going to eat?

00:24:50.251 --> 00:24:51.442
This place is famous.

00:24:52.661 --> 00:24:54.461
Is this the place you wanted to come to?

00:24:54.841 --> 00:24:55.559
Let's eat.

00:24:57.572 --> 00:24:59.196
I'm not a big fan of tteokbokki.

00:25:00.591 --> 00:25:03.801
Han Sunho doesn't have likes or dislikes.

00:25:04.126 --> 00:25:05.126
Just eat the tteokbokki.

00:25:09.127 --> 00:25:10.127
"Ahh."

00:25:16.668 --> 00:25:17.668
"Ahh..."

00:25:18.476 --> 00:25:19.550
What if I don't want to eat tteokbokki?

00:25:20.661 --> 00:25:23.281
So, should we just
give up on one agency...

00:25:35.647 --> 00:25:36.387
What's that?

00:25:39.227 --> 00:25:40.057
What's what?

00:25:42.091 --> 00:25:43.341
There was something there.

00:25:45.850 --> 00:25:47.571
Gosh, I almost got caught.

00:25:47.996 --> 00:25:48.996
Oh my gosh.

00:25:59.279 --> 00:26:00.064
Let's head out.

00:26:01.045 --> 00:26:01.853
We're leaving already?

00:26:13.176 --> 00:26:15.046
Why did we come here if we're not eating?

00:26:15.446 --> 00:26:17.271
We have lots to do besides this.

00:26:17.518 --> 00:26:18.155
What?

00:26:23.193 --> 00:26:26.356
Do you really think
people won't recognize you like that?

00:26:26.477 --> 00:26:27.997
Just mind your own business.

00:26:29.011 --> 00:26:31.352
Anyway, standing next to me now,

00:26:31.374 --> 00:26:33.130
anyone can tell
you're Han Sunho.

00:26:41.199 --> 00:26:41.800
Hey.

00:26:41.822 --> 00:26:42.900
What's this?

00:26:43.361 --> 00:26:44.248
What's what?

00:26:45.411 --> 00:26:46.470
Why are you doing this to me?

00:26:46.590 --> 00:26:48.274
Just stay put, Han Sunho.

00:26:48.566 --> 00:26:49.665
Can you take it easy?

00:26:49.696 --> 00:26:51.440
Can you back off a bit?

00:26:51.512 --> 00:26:53.300
Why are you doing this to me, seriously?

00:26:53.322 --> 00:26:55.146
Why don't you ever listen?

00:26:55.168 --> 00:26:56.565
You really don't get it!

00:26:56.587 --> 00:26:58.450
You never listen, Han Sunho!

00:26:59.156 --> 00:27:00.475
Stop doing this, seriously!

00:27:00.503 --> 00:27:01.645
Stop what?

00:27:02.947 --> 00:27:04.762
Thanks for the meal, everyone.

00:27:05.945 --> 00:27:07.785
Sunho likes meat too.

00:27:08.815 --> 00:27:10.888
I wonder if he's eating while working?

00:27:11.951 --> 00:27:14.231
What kind of person is Mr. Han?

00:27:14.541 --> 00:27:15.853
Mr. Han is quite popular, right?

00:27:15.941 --> 00:27:16.846
Of course!

00:27:17.131 --> 00:27:19.043
That's why you brought Sunho here.

00:27:19.721 --> 00:27:21.179
Absolutely!

00:27:21.431 --> 00:27:22.212
Still,

00:27:22.235 --> 00:27:25.842
there's a lot we don't
know about Mr. Han...

00:27:27.042 --> 00:27:28.481
What's Mr. Han like usually?

00:27:29.176 --> 00:27:32.276
I bet it's different from
what people usually see.

00:27:34.325 --> 00:27:38.320
On the outside,
he seems cold and stubborn,

00:27:38.770 --> 00:27:41.599
but he's actually very kind
and warm-hearted.

00:27:41.621 --> 00:27:43.311
He has a surprisingly cute side too.

00:27:45.963 --> 00:27:47.488
Sunho has a sleeping habit...

00:27:47.510 --> 00:27:48.641
Manager Han!

00:27:51.273 --> 00:27:52.273
Are you okay?

00:28:01.342 --> 00:28:03.530
But why are you asking?

00:28:03.553 --> 00:28:06.150
Where did Mr. Han go
with Director Yun?

00:28:06.173 --> 00:28:08.245
Are they attending an official event?

00:28:08.392 --> 00:28:11.051
What was Park Jungwon
doing here originally?

00:28:12.959 --> 00:28:13.959
Well...

00:28:15.768 --> 00:28:16.768
Manager Han,

00:28:17.225 --> 00:28:19.921
how was it meeting Mina in person?

00:28:22.150 --> 00:28:23.020
Of course...!

00:28:25.995 --> 00:28:26.864
It's nice.

00:28:31.696 --> 00:28:34.625
What kind of dating style
does Mr. Han have?

00:28:34.648 --> 00:28:36.289
I'm really curious, right?

00:28:37.226 --> 00:28:39.051
- Sunho is...
- What about you, Baekho?

00:28:43.218 --> 00:28:45.929
What's your style, Baekho?

00:28:53.044 --> 00:28:54.422
Wow!

00:28:54.979 --> 00:28:56.096
What's that?

00:28:56.196 --> 00:28:57.995
Should we check it out?
It's really cool.

00:28:58.017 --> 00:28:58.502
What's there?

00:28:58.524 --> 00:28:59.524
Let's go quickly.

00:29:00.046 --> 00:29:00.911
What's there?

00:29:01.411 --> 00:29:04.318
There's something really cool we have to
see together, but Sunho left his phone.

00:29:04.340 --> 00:29:05.441
What's there?

00:29:06.404 --> 00:29:07.437
Yukyung,

00:29:09.737 --> 00:29:11.515
why did you interrupt the flow?

00:29:12.003 --> 00:29:12.616
Uh.

00:29:12.877 --> 00:29:14.071
I'm sorry.

00:29:14.301 --> 00:29:15.931
I did it without realizing...

00:29:17.081 --> 00:29:18.762
Let's not let our guard down.

00:29:19.162 --> 00:29:19.901
Got it?

00:29:19.971 --> 00:29:20.657
Yes.

00:29:21.531 --> 00:29:22.439
Let's go!

00:29:34.354 --> 00:29:37.574
It seems like they want to find out
something about Mr. Han.

00:29:37.701 --> 00:29:40.967
It looks like they're trying to
do something with Sunho.

00:29:41.361 --> 00:29:43.420
Those people are really suspicious.

00:29:43.845 --> 00:29:47.180
The fact that they used the word
"portrait rights" is also strange.

00:29:49.980 --> 00:29:51.771
Those people are weird...

00:29:52.681 --> 00:29:54.251
Those people are suspicious...

00:30:02.159 --> 00:30:03.360
Do you think they noticed something?

00:30:03.651 --> 00:30:05.495
I don't think so yet.

00:30:06.214 --> 00:30:07.084
Here,

00:30:07.963 --> 00:30:11.701
photos and videos of
Mr. Han collected over three years.

00:30:21.193 --> 00:30:23.281
I didn't gather this data for this...

00:30:23.882 --> 00:30:24.569
Oh no.

00:30:25.322 --> 00:30:29.656
Let's create a prototype of
Mr. Han based on the existing data.

00:30:30.302 --> 00:30:31.076
Okay.

00:30:31.739 --> 00:30:32.570
Okay...

00:30:41.263 --> 00:30:42.341
Han Sunho,

00:30:46.978 --> 00:30:47.825
let's go.

00:30:49.141 --> 00:30:49.967
Again?

00:30:52.760 --> 00:30:53.738
Han Sunho.

00:31:03.973 --> 00:31:06.978
How should Mr. Han's dating style be?

00:31:07.078 --> 00:31:10.425
I thought it would be
very kind and attentive.

00:31:10.447 --> 00:31:12.189
Did Director Yun arrive?

00:31:14.992 --> 00:31:16.891
Oh? Jooyeon, you're here early.

00:31:20.459 --> 00:31:21.601
Han Sunho,

00:31:26.145 --> 00:31:26.877
let's go.

00:31:33.036 --> 00:31:33.925
Let's go.

00:31:36.271 --> 00:31:37.061
Yes.

00:31:37.317 --> 00:31:38.803
Let's go, let's go.

00:31:39.203 --> 00:31:40.776
How's the current physique?

00:31:40.798 --> 00:31:45.296
Yeah, you have a good build,
since Mr. Han is tall, let's use that...

00:31:51.096 --> 00:31:52.961
Why is Han Sunho here so early?

00:31:54.097 --> 00:31:55.097
Let's go.

00:31:57.491 --> 00:31:59.358
Put this on.

00:32:00.310 --> 00:32:01.165
What's this?

00:32:04.691 --> 00:32:05.961
How am I supposed to wear this?

00:32:06.164 --> 00:32:08.054
Hey, hey!

00:32:15.772 --> 00:32:17.486
What is that outfit?

00:32:26.658 --> 00:32:28.552
What have you been up to lately?

00:32:29.449 --> 00:32:30.829
I have no idea.

00:32:31.186 --> 00:32:33.265
Am I working or dating?

00:32:36.607 --> 00:32:37.380
What about the company?

00:32:38.162 --> 00:32:39.163
Did you find out anything?

00:32:39.751 --> 00:32:40.658
Not yet.

00:32:42.687 --> 00:32:46.010
It seems like
it's related to 'ForMe Version 2'.

00:32:46.590 --> 00:32:47.471
Version 2?

00:32:48.457 --> 00:32:51.086
It's the new version
being launched by 'It's You'.

00:32:51.793 --> 00:32:53.754
You can even see it with your eyes!

00:32:56.094 --> 00:32:57.354
You can see 'ForMe Version 2'?

00:32:57.696 --> 00:33:00.991
Yeah, that's why I've been
meeting with Mina every day.

00:33:02.427 --> 00:33:05.447
What does she plan to do
with my portrait rights?

00:33:05.614 --> 00:33:08.294
Anyway, it's already been a week.

00:33:08.451 --> 00:33:10.121
Let's finish the contract and get out.

00:33:10.702 --> 00:33:12.296
We need to bring Mina out too.

00:33:16.206 --> 00:33:18.242
Try bringing that weird thing home!

00:33:18.541 --> 00:33:19.662
You'll be kicked out.

00:33:24.777 --> 00:33:26.022
Weird thing?

00:33:26.045 --> 00:33:27.038
Watch your words.

00:33:27.060 --> 00:33:29.833
Isn't it weird if it's not even a person?

00:33:29.898 --> 00:33:32.447
Did you lose your girlfriend
to that weird thing?

00:33:32.515 --> 00:33:33.655
What did you just say?

00:33:35.085 --> 00:33:36.085
Say that again.

00:33:37.193 --> 00:33:38.882
Why, did I say something wrong?

00:33:38.976 --> 00:33:39.830
Uh...

00:33:40.501 --> 00:33:42.186
It's been a while since you got hit, huh?

00:33:42.261 --> 00:33:43.041
Don't come.

00:33:43.391 --> 00:33:44.161
Don't come.

00:33:44.611 --> 00:33:45.342
Don't do it!

00:33:45.801 --> 00:33:46.490
Don't do it!

00:33:46.617 --> 00:33:50.607
No!

00:33:54.836 --> 00:33:56.039
What's today about?

00:33:56.556 --> 00:33:58.108
Just a simple interview.

00:34:06.678 --> 00:34:07.464
Sunho!

00:34:07.487 --> 00:34:09.229
You're not really
dating that woman, right?

00:34:09.251 --> 00:34:09.790
Right?

00:34:09.812 --> 00:34:11.049
We trust you!

00:34:11.071 --> 00:34:12.809
Please let us in!

00:34:12.832 --> 00:34:13.977
We'll just look, okay?

00:34:14.236 --> 00:34:15.598
Let us in...

00:34:15.621 --> 00:34:16.780
You don't have to stop them.

00:34:27.091 --> 00:34:28.405
It's crazy, right?

00:34:28.501 --> 00:34:32.989
The rumor about Mr. Han's public romance
after his retirement to focus on writing.

00:34:33.031 --> 00:34:34.871
Some even say he retired to date.

00:34:34.905 --> 00:34:38.028
Seeing you two together officially,
is the rumor true, Mr. Han?

00:34:38.199 --> 00:34:41.418
Is that even a question?

00:34:41.506 --> 00:34:44.148
Sunho would never do that.

00:34:44.481 --> 00:34:46.349
What are you talking about?

00:34:46.371 --> 00:34:47.718
Don't make Sunho look bad!

00:34:47.740 --> 00:34:49.145
What are you saying?

00:34:49.167 --> 00:34:51.054
Don't make Sunho look bad!

00:34:52.291 --> 00:34:55.711
First, I'd like to sincerely
apologize to the fans.

00:34:56.764 --> 00:34:57.527
No.

00:34:58.001 --> 00:35:00.531
I'll do the apologizing.

00:35:01.161 --> 00:35:05.511
The romance rumor was an article
released unilaterally by 'It's You'.

00:35:05.694 --> 00:35:07.269
For your sake.

00:35:10.266 --> 00:35:15.078
Were you upset about the romance rumor
between me and Han Sunho?

00:35:15.686 --> 00:35:17.141
And were you jealous?

00:35:17.241 --> 00:35:19.171
What is she even saying?

00:35:19.193 --> 00:35:20.681
Is that even a statement?

00:35:20.711 --> 00:35:21.957
This is ridiculous.

00:35:22.357 --> 00:35:23.469
If she says...

00:35:23.491 --> 00:35:27.463
Now, I'll make it possible for you
to date Han Sunho.

00:35:27.833 --> 00:35:29.123
Just like me.

00:35:33.473 --> 00:35:35.601
Introducing for the first time to you all,

00:35:36.071 --> 00:35:39.705
the first look at 'ForMe Version 2'
from 'It's You'.

00:35:40.165 --> 00:35:40.917
And it's...

00:35:41.892 --> 00:35:43.101
Han Sunho.

00:35:45.957 --> 00:35:47.158
When is 'ForMe Version 2' being released?

00:35:47.180 --> 00:35:48.735
When is 'ForMe Version 2' coming out?

00:35:48.757 --> 00:35:50.532
Can we see it soon?

00:35:50.554 --> 00:35:51.657
Sunho, we love you!

00:35:56.986 --> 00:35:59.556
Release the article and
ad for 'ForMe Version 2'.

00:36:00.042 --> 00:36:01.617
Yes, understood.

00:36:02.646 --> 00:36:05.948
Yes, please upload the article
about Mr. Han and 'ForMe Version 2' now.

00:36:05.970 --> 00:36:07.240
The romance article?

00:36:07.550 --> 00:36:09.640
Yes, you can take it down now.

00:36:09.741 --> 00:36:13.684
You'll be able to experience
the 'ForMe Version 2' demo next week.

00:36:15.031 --> 00:36:17.809
Only at 'It's You'.

00:36:17.864 --> 00:36:20.344
That article?
You can take it down now.

00:36:20.366 --> 00:36:22.421
What does that mean?

00:36:23.782 --> 00:36:25.856
The Mina that Mr. Han sees.

00:36:26.756 --> 00:36:27.810
What about Mina?

00:36:29.281 --> 00:36:32.469
It's what weeting Mr. Han
like that is to everyone.

00:36:33.206 --> 00:36:33.950
What?

00:36:34.942 --> 00:36:37.174
Is this the project you're doing
using my portrait rights?

00:36:37.316 --> 00:36:38.175
Are you kidding me?

00:36:39.841 --> 00:36:43.174
Did you think I paid all that money

00:36:43.196 --> 00:36:44.941
just to have meals
and chat with you?

00:36:46.259 --> 00:36:50.321
I absolutely won't allow it,
so cancel the contract if you want.

00:36:50.421 --> 00:36:51.361
Fine.

00:36:51.811 --> 00:36:54.644
Then get ready to pay the penalty.

00:36:55.523 --> 00:36:57.210
Are you threatening me right now?

00:37:01.230 --> 00:37:04.414
I paid a fair price for the rights.

00:37:04.470 --> 00:37:06.659
You signed the contract.

00:37:06.959 --> 00:37:10.521
Do I really have to keep explaining
this obvious thing?

00:37:25.174 --> 00:37:27.539
Even in a world full of fakes,

00:37:27.980 --> 00:37:30.540
this is the lowest quality fake I've seen.

00:37:30.656 --> 00:37:31.641
Fake?

00:37:31.994 --> 00:37:34.651
You people who are
broken up might need it.

00:37:35.028 --> 00:37:37.614
An eternal love with no expiration date.

00:37:37.761 --> 00:37:40.750
If you put in that many preservatives,
of course, it won't expire.

00:37:41.071 --> 00:37:42.776
But it's harmful to the body.

00:37:42.822 --> 00:37:44.182
Why don't you try it?

00:37:44.406 --> 00:37:46.590
It's very good for mental health.

00:37:49.084 --> 00:37:51.140
I don't know why it came to this,

00:37:51.590 --> 00:37:53.671
but are you scared of
forming relationships?

00:37:53.941 --> 00:37:55.891
All that one-hour stuff is just an excuse.

00:37:56.041 --> 00:37:57.145
What did you say?

00:37:57.212 --> 00:37:59.532
You're actually afraid of getting hurt,
right?

00:38:00.182 --> 00:38:01.392
Scared in advance.

00:38:03.986 --> 00:38:05.776
What do you know about me?

00:38:05.876 --> 00:38:08.905
Hiding behind a convincingly made-up front,
pretending not to be lonely.

00:38:10.207 --> 00:38:11.094
Isn't that right?

00:38:16.779 --> 00:38:17.593
What's this?

00:38:18.189 --> 00:38:19.320
What's happening?

00:38:20.928 --> 00:38:21.928
Facility Team here.

00:38:22.081 --> 00:38:23.081
What's the issue?

00:38:23.346 --> 00:38:25.101
The elevator is stuck here.

00:38:25.411 --> 00:38:26.136
What?

00:38:26.555 --> 00:38:27.509
I'll be there quickly.

00:38:27.531 --> 00:38:28.531
Please wait a moment.

00:38:32.274 --> 00:38:36.361
Doesn't your perfect AI boyfriend come to
the rescue at times like this?

00:38:42.108 --> 00:38:43.541
What's going on? What's wrong?

00:38:49.626 --> 00:38:50.626
Hey!

00:38:51.943 --> 00:38:53.243
Isn't there anyone outside?

00:38:54.221 --> 00:38:55.144
Hey!

00:38:59.522 --> 00:39:00.717
Isn't there anyone?

00:39:09.216 --> 00:39:10.153
Once.

00:39:11.919 --> 00:39:14.201
It must have been a coincidence.

00:39:21.058 --> 00:39:23.371
Yun Bia, snap out of it.

00:39:23.981 --> 00:39:25.088
Look at me!

00:39:25.960 --> 00:39:26.960
Yun Bia!

00:39:27.315 --> 00:39:28.144
Me!

00:39:31.460 --> 00:39:32.525
Are you okay?

00:39:32.998 --> 00:39:33.857
Twice.

00:39:34.689 --> 00:39:35.514
Maybe...

00:39:36.232 --> 00:39:38.555
this isn't just a coincidence.

00:40:04.061 --> 00:40:06.086
Maybe I can...

00:40:06.800 --> 00:40:09.201
trust my fate with this man.

00:40:11.691 --> 00:40:13.421
Even if it's a foolish hope.

00:40:26.954 --> 00:40:28.054
Bia!

00:40:34.070 --> 00:40:35.192
[Department of Mental Health]

00:40:35.216 --> 00:40:38.517
The test results didn't show
much improvement,

00:40:39.744 --> 00:40:44.301
and again, you realized
it was an hour later?

00:40:46.641 --> 00:40:47.651
Again?

00:40:50.611 --> 00:40:51.611
Yes.

00:40:51.961 --> 00:40:56.140
At first, I thought it was a coincidence
when I collapsed after an hour,

00:40:57.140 --> 00:41:00.251
but this time,
I didn't lose consciousness.

00:41:03.251 --> 00:41:06.791
Was there anything in common
in both situations?

00:41:09.941 --> 00:41:12.291
I was with the same person.

00:41:16.820 --> 00:41:17.880
Yun Bia.

00:41:20.461 --> 00:41:22.351
Why didn't you tell me?

00:41:23.901 --> 00:41:27.081
It's foolish to rely on coincidences.

00:41:27.481 --> 00:41:29.680
Is that all I am to you?

00:41:30.344 --> 00:41:31.947
Less than the company, no,

00:41:32.834 --> 00:41:34.598
less than Han Sunho?

00:41:34.871 --> 00:41:36.501
Hey, what are you saying...

00:41:37.421 --> 00:41:38.382
It's not that...

00:41:38.404 --> 00:41:40.763
Staying cooped up at home,
unable to meet anyone,

00:41:41.133 --> 00:41:44.163
1 minute, 2 minutes, 10 minutes, 1 hour.

00:41:46.291 --> 00:41:48.931
We worked together to get this far.

00:41:49.621 --> 00:41:52.277
I just want you to be happy.

00:41:52.977 --> 00:41:54.951
I don't want you to struggle.

00:41:55.096 --> 00:41:56.226
I know...

00:41:57.186 --> 00:42:00.256
That's why I'm always grateful to you.

00:42:02.861 --> 00:42:03.930
We agreed...

00:42:04.487 --> 00:42:07.619
to live without secrets,

00:42:08.794 --> 00:42:11.421
relying on each other like that, right?

00:42:12.871 --> 00:42:14.931
Yeah, that's right.

00:42:14.961 --> 00:42:17.406
Then why didn't you tell me?

00:42:18.006 --> 00:42:19.791
Are you not relying on me anymore?

00:42:20.066 --> 00:42:21.294
What are you talking about?

00:42:21.316 --> 00:42:22.726
You're all I have.

00:42:26.416 --> 00:42:27.856
I won't hide anything from you again.

00:42:28.711 --> 00:42:30.301
I won't make you worry.

00:42:36.191 --> 00:42:37.191
Alright.

00:42:38.839 --> 00:42:40.398
Just go home for now.

00:42:41.353 --> 00:42:43.006
Rest and we'll talk tomorrow.

00:42:43.961 --> 00:42:45.941
Please don't be mad, okay?

00:42:55.487 --> 00:42:56.579
[It's said that CEO Yun Bia
always wears a timer]

00:42:56.604 --> 00:42:57.776
[There’s also a theory that
she collapses after an hour]

00:42:57.801 --> 00:42:58.925
[I wish I could disappear
every hour at work too...]

00:42:58.972 --> 00:42:59.858
[I can't stand overtime every day]

00:42:59.883 --> 00:43:01.462
[Disappearing every hour might even
be a high-level marketing strategy]

00:43:01.487 --> 00:43:02.488
[Seriously, where does
she go after an hour?]

00:43:02.513 --> 00:43:03.560
[Someone I know also gets
anxious at certain times...]

00:43:03.585 --> 00:43:04.782
[Maybe the CEO of 'It's You'
has panic attack symptoms too]

00:43:08.322 --> 00:43:10.184
[An ill-advised person.
An hour of her. Panic symptoms]

00:43:10.209 --> 00:43:12.488
[Fell down?
One hour. Timer... Secret?]

00:43:12.513 --> 00:43:14.446
[Why in front of me?
Twice?]

00:43:15.431 --> 00:43:17.881
Doesn't anyone know there's
something wrong with Director Yun?

00:43:31.939 --> 00:43:32.939
What's all this?

00:43:33.101 --> 00:43:35.659
I'll find a lawyer right away,
don't worry.

00:43:35.681 --> 00:43:38.041
This is clearly a fraudulent contract.

00:43:38.109 --> 00:43:40.721
Both Jiyoung and I packed up and left.

00:43:43.898 --> 00:43:45.480
What about your AI girlfriend?

00:43:46.816 --> 00:43:47.480
What?

00:43:47.680 --> 00:43:48.886
You said you'd bring her out.

00:43:48.977 --> 00:43:49.977
Oh, right.

00:43:50.876 --> 00:43:52.073
Mina!

00:43:54.368 --> 00:43:55.526
I'll come get you!

00:44:01.320 --> 00:44:03.201
What do you know about me?

00:44:04.061 --> 00:44:07.385
Hiding behind a convincingly made-up front,
pretending not to be lonely.

00:44:08.485 --> 00:44:09.485
Isn't it?

00:44:21.972 --> 00:44:24.501
I was with someone like that.

00:44:24.691 --> 00:44:27.721
Do you feel any psychological comfort
with that person?

00:44:28.891 --> 00:44:29.891
Not at all.

00:44:30.871 --> 00:44:31.994
With just two times,

00:44:32.016 --> 00:44:35.871
it's hard to hastily judge that
the symptoms have improved.

00:44:36.501 --> 00:44:38.911
It's better not to have
too high expectations.

00:44:49.295 --> 00:44:50.651
Yes, this is Yun Bia.

00:44:52.221 --> 00:44:53.784
Director, there's a big problem!

00:44:53.806 --> 00:44:55.781
You should come to the office right away.

00:44:58.283 --> 00:45:03.313
After Han's news, simultaneous user surge
and it seems the server is overloaded.

00:45:04.708 --> 00:45:06.751
If it's just an overload issue,
that's a relief.

00:45:07.181 --> 00:45:08.711
Can you restore the server by morning?

00:45:08.737 --> 00:45:09.328
Yes.

00:45:10.031 --> 00:45:11.441
But more than that...

00:45:13.841 --> 00:45:14.410
What?

00:45:14.432 --> 00:45:15.781
Is there another problem?

00:45:16.867 --> 00:45:17.986
Director!

00:45:18.305 --> 00:45:19.625
What's going on with the company?

00:45:19.681 --> 00:45:21.266
There's a problem with the server.

00:45:21.966 --> 00:45:22.966
The server?

00:45:24.463 --> 00:45:27.071
So what's the biggest issue right now?

00:45:27.771 --> 00:45:30.821
It seems someone tried to
breach our firewall.

00:45:31.221 --> 00:45:32.581
Is it from a competitor?

00:45:33.581 --> 00:45:35.281
What about the data for 'ForMe Version 2'?

00:45:35.571 --> 00:45:37.601
Is Mr. Han's prototype okay?

00:45:38.106 --> 00:45:40.347
The Version 2 prototype...

00:45:43.274 --> 00:45:44.951
has been completely reset.

00:45:45.251 --> 00:45:46.280
Everything?

00:45:46.780 --> 00:45:48.740
Yes, probably.

00:45:50.956 --> 00:45:52.521
Yun Bia, where are you going?

00:46:03.846 --> 00:46:05.331
Why did I say that?

00:46:12.708 --> 00:46:14.543
The customer is not answering the phone.

00:46:14.565 --> 00:46:17.391
After the beep,
you'll be connected to voicemail.

00:46:40.273 --> 00:46:41.731
Who are you?

00:46:55.389 --> 00:46:56.971
Excuse me, Yun Bia?

00:47:01.003 --> 00:47:02.493
You didn't faint again, did you?

00:47:11.522 --> 00:47:12.781
Bia, are you here?

00:47:18.868 --> 00:47:20.071
I'm sorry.

00:47:23.191 --> 00:47:25.231
I'm a colleague of Yun Bia's from work.

00:47:26.461 --> 00:47:27.951
The door was open.

00:47:28.266 --> 00:47:30.126
It's okay, come in.

00:47:39.633 --> 00:47:41.551
Sorry for dropping by unannounced.

00:47:47.129 --> 00:47:49.451
I was worried about Yun Bia.

00:47:57.202 --> 00:47:58.205
Han Sunho?

00:48:13.668 --> 00:48:14.558
Sunae?

00:48:15.891 --> 00:48:16.931
Aunt Sunae?